That's 16. Quinn and MF are hardly ever played as ADC's. I've seen way more mid MF's than I've seen of ADC MF's since her horrible rework. 

With ten bans, you can ban every single ADC with mobility, thus destroying the role and turning this back into League of Burst where everyone rolls super bursty/dive-y champs. We're finally in a meta where a lot more champions can be used. So many tanks can be picked, tank destroyers, peelers, immobile mages and ADCs... Before, we had nothing but mobility, now we can use just about anything. Ten bans will just end up killing it all by banning out tanks or any kind of mobile ADC or simply make mid useless. Like... Seriously.
